{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BishopPainBlur}}
'''A_BishopPainBlur'''

(no parameters)

Has a 25% chance of jumping to the Blur state, otherwise spawns a {{Class|BishopPainBlur}} actor near the calling actor's current location.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|Bishop}} and actors inheriting from it.

